{"tid":1148831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手買保險] 想買自願醫保，新個隻Bowtie 好唔好？","createTime":"2019-05-10T17:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T07:11:29.000Z","uid":253038,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cb8cf0f35f20bdab333033ef3edf58dff59d6291","tid":1148831,"uid":253038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:04:51.000Z","msg":"想買自願醫保好耐，但仲諗緊邊隻好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前睇過下BUPA 同 AIA <br />\n但今日收工坐車見到 bowtie 有個廣告，上網望左兩望見佢又上網買， 又話曾俊華BACKUP咁<br />\n是但就咁上去QUOTE 左下價  ＄153 好似又幾平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LTaVAAI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLTaVAAI.png&h=e85a49b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見佢上網買好似好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之前睇過D POST 話平過哂咁多間大行<br />\n我唔係好識保險，但我見之前佢個廣告又懶係SELL 後生 又潮潮地咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打絲打 覺得其實 有無聽過BOWTIE ? 其實買唔買得過？ 同埋覺得好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n利申：自己畢左業後除左以前份學生保， 如果自己公司個份唔計，就其實無買過保險既<br />\n個人自己平時就無咩病痛，但唔係好識點睇保險 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50bc4d6cb0d0c6ed86342710da04941c01c9b1f0","tid":1148831,"uid":82243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:06:40.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"23b5cac79e228fe40f59c5ca53104d9b4538479c","tid":1148831,"uid":253038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:12:32.000Z","msg":"問多樣 其實如果唔想比D Agent 約黎SELL 唔等使野，係咪自己上網買好D？"},{"pid":"21cd521485ec9ba492393c6011c2799277803eb3","tid":1148831,"uid":140018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:14:20.000Z","msg":"上網買其實都有agent跟"},{"pid":"06f525e10e0ad20d1e2427b335eb367e89c05e1b","tid":1148831,"uid":8854,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:22:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ca506b8d5b0e631a62f878c89e264762cc0259e","tid":1148831,"uid":253038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21cd521485ec9ba492393c6011c2799277803eb3","tid":1148831,"uid":140018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:14:20.000Z","msg":"上網買其實都有agent跟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:43:07.000Z","msg":"我見佢係咁寫ja <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  中介人 我估係agent <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n在自願醫保產品方面，Bowtie對比其他傳統保險公司有何優勢？<br />\n由於Bowtie是純網上營運，投保、保單服務、索償均可於網上完成。純網上運作有助減低我們的營運及行政成本，加上Bowtie不設中介人，故我們能以較低的保費承保。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即使Bowtie提供的是純網上保險，我們提供的服務與傳統保險公司一樣，包括設有客戶服務中心、索償助理、醫療團隊等售前售後支援。我們亦首創了BowtieCash獎賞計劃*，以減輕客戶的醫療開支負擔。<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.bowtie.com.hk/zh/vhis/standard-plan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bowtie.com.hk%2Fzh%2Fvhis%2Fstandard-plan&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYE6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=ae9e848f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bowtie.com.hk/zh/vhis/standard-plan</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"659f8e5af5936e1e0564698e7361d7431de4181f","tid":1148831,"uid":253038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"06f525e10e0ad20d1e2427b335eb367e89c05e1b","tid":1148831,"uid":8854,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"cb8cf0f35f20bdab333033ef3edf58dff59d6291","tid":1148831,"uid":253038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:04:51.000Z","msg":"想買自願醫保好耐，但仲諗緊邊隻好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前睇過下BUPA 同 AIA <br />\n但今日收工坐車見到 bowtie 有個廣告，上網望左兩望見佢又上網買， 又話曾俊華BACKUP咁<br />\n是但就咁上去QUOTE 左下價  ＄153 好似又幾平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LTaVAAI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLTaVAAI.png&h=e85a49b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見佢上網買好似好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之前睇過D POST 話平過哂咁多間大行<br />\n我唔係好識保險，但我見之前佢個廣告又懶係SELL 後生 又潮潮地咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打絲打 覺得其實 有無聽過BOWTIE ? 其實買唔買得過？ 同埋覺得好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n利申：自己畢左業後除左以前份學生保， 如果自己公司個份唔計，就其實無買過保險既<br />\n個人自己平時就無咩病痛，但唔係好識點睇保險 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:22:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:46:44.000Z","msg":"點解 agent 可以搵醫生 book 床位<br />\n自己book 係咪唔得？ <br />\n<br />\n住院鐘數係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋呢 靈活同平時d 醫保有咩唔同 ？"},{"pid":"7cacaf17e77303a3fe89996615ed4a4596d3e36a","tid":1148831,"uid":8854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T18:33:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8aabebb9cf3fcea9e7e407ba8f6eed6917ee7253","tid":1148831,"uid":8854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T18:38:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c285ca404ccefd18f8ad3c390ff215c389118f3c","tid":1148831,"uid":253038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T03:16:42.000Z","msg":"咁其實照師兄咁講<br />\n自願醫保標準應該間間都一樣  <br />\n<br />\n咁其實除左價錢揀邊間有無分別 ？ <br />\n諗緊係咪就咁買左標準先加上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除左樓上師兄講有agent 同你揀醫生之外<br />\n<br />\n因為我見Bowtie 廣告有個護士咁既物體 係隔離<br />\n我估有醫療團隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n咁其實係咪其他公司都係得agent 做對頭人？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5104085bb1de93ff6b0905e20eaf3c0f4797c5ad","tid":1148831,"uid":41867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aabebb9cf3fcea9e7e407ba8f6eed6917ee7253","tid":1148831,"uid":8854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cacaf17e77303a3fe89996615e