"tid":1148831,"uid":161767,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"659f8e5af5936e1e0564698e7361d7431de4181f","tid":1148831,"uid":253038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"06f525e10e0ad20d1e2427b335eb367e89c05e1b","tid":1148831,"uid":8854,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"cb8cf0f35f20bdab333033ef3edf58dff59d6291","tid":1148831,"uid":253038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:04:51.000Z","msg":"想買自願醫保好耐，但仲諗緊邊隻好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前睇過下BUPA 同 AIA <br />\n但今日收工坐車見到 bowtie 有個廣告，上網望左兩望見佢又上網買， 又話曾俊華BACKUP咁<br />\n是但就咁上去QUOTE 左下價  ＄153 好似又幾平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LTaVAAI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLTaVAAI.png&h=e85a49b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見佢上網買好似好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之前睇過D POST 話平過哂咁多間大行<br />\n我唔係好識保險，但我見之前佢個廣告又懶係SELL 後生 又潮潮地咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打絲打 覺得其實 有無聽過BOWTIE ? 其實買唔買得過？ 同埋覺得好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n利申：自己畢左業後除左以前份學生保， 如果自己公司個份唔計，就其實無買過保險既<br />\n個人自己平時就無咩病痛，但唔係好識點睇保險 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:22:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:46:44.000Z","msg":"點解 agent 可以搵醫生 book 床位<br />\n自己book 係咪唔得？ <br />\n<br />\n住院鐘數係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋呢 靈活同平時d 醫保有咩唔同 ？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:52:30.000Z","msg":"自己book實得<br />\n自己遞埋form搞claim我借多謝你添<br />\n<br />\n咁我病到九彩都係想病個agent幫我settle好晒d野等我唔駛煩<br />\n唔係做乜要幫agent買<br />\nAgent要湊客就係咁解<br />\n生仔去邊間醫院要知<br />\n連買樓買邊區都俾埋advice<br />\n有時癲到婆媳糾紛都要問你點解決<br />\n你都要答到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：前銀行狗<img src=\"/assets